+
+## Added
+
+- `runtime.scheduler_route_adapter`
+- `SchedulerRouteRequest`
+- `SchedulerRouteReply`
+- `handle_scheduler_route_request()`
+- `scheduler_route_request_mapping()`
+- adapter event topic:
